product_desc:
w-CHARGING project will create a recharge service Mobile Phone consuming the credit telephone.Each user must also purchase a miniaturized device that will connect to the phone every time the need arises and charging also subscribe to the service. This requires collaboration with the telephone operators. the application works in two phases:
- Subscription: the customer subscribes to the service by USSD command after you buy the wavelength conversion device in electromagnetic electric current;
- Charging: the client sends the USSD command to the server. this one makes a paging and sends a command to the BTS transmitter so that the latter sends the electromagnetic wave branch kit on the client's phone. the kit makes the conversion and the phone is charging.
